      "id": "PopularPost350306",
      "post_content": "Why is this so poorly rated? Play it for ![3](/Handlers/Image.ashx?size=small&name=3&type=symbol) as a 2/2 and at any time you can pay 3 to make it a 5/1 or 1/5. Now, this isn't the best blue creature out there, but certainly useful. If he's unblocked, or you want to kill a blocker you can have 5 damage, if you get blocked or are being attacked you can always swap to 1/5. ",
